  "text": "Under some measurement strategies, the internal and external electrodes work together. A 3D model was used to test the performance of the inner-outer sensor. Six different inner-outer sensor types were designed with different characteristics such as size, number and distribution of the internal electrodes. The 3D reconstruction results showed that the inner-outer sensor have better reconstruction performance than the conventional sensor with only external electrodes [CITATION_1] .",
